</li>
<li><h3>Subcellular Localizations</h3>
An integrated dataset of 9 subcellular localization databases including 269 586 subcellular localizations.<br /> <a href="{{ path('ComppiDescriptionBundle_help') }}/input_loc">Details...</a>
</li>
<li><h3>Species</h3>
A comparative assessment of four species: <i>S. cerevisiae</i>, <i>C. elegans</i>, <i>D. melanogaster</i>, <i>H. sapiens</i><br />
<a href="{{ path('ComppiDescriptionBundle_help') }}/species">Details...</a>
</li>
<li><h3>1600+ Gene Ontology Cellular Component Terms</h3>
A hierarchic structure of subcellular localizations using more than 1600 Gene Ontology cellular component terms. <br /><a href="{{ path('ComppiDescriptionBundle_help') }}/subcell_locs">Details...</a>
</li>
<li><h3>Interaction and Localization Score</h3>
A localization score for the proteins and an interaction score for the protein-protein interactions comprising data-quality and interactome-consensus of subcellular localization. <br />
<a href="{{ path('ComppiDescriptionBundle_help') }}/scores">Details...</a>
</li>
<li><h3>Protein Search</h3>
Direct search options for individual proteins with autocomplete function. <br />
<a href="{{ path('ComppiDescriptionBundle_help') }}/protein_search">Details...</a>
</li>
<li><h3>Download of Custom Datasets</h3>
Download options of whole-proteome or organelle-specific interactomes and of integrated protein-protein interaction and subcellular localization datasets. <br /><a href="{{ path('ComppiDescriptionBundle_help') }}/downloads">Details...</a>
